description.narrative: UNICEF social policy focused on disability including to support the development of a new law for persons with disability. The Palestinian Authority will present the first State Party report to the CRC committee in January 2020, following UNICEF engagement with the Geneva committee through a UNCT confidential report and presentation at the pre-sessional committee meeting. UNICEF also supported the PA to submit their first report on the CRPD. Evidence generation continued to be central to UNICEF programming including with data collection for the MICS. UNICEF has invested in effective management responses to evaluations to ensure programme quality. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:20/01/2020
